Information

The bay of wonders.

Majestic panoramas, breath-taking geographical phenomena and an ecosystem offering an amazing biodiversity: a guided tour of the Bay of Fundy with Alain Clavette. It is also said that this vast sound, lying on Canada's Atlantic coast, has the largest tidal range in the world.
